  DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN

    The iiccoo(1X11R5) utility displays a wire-frame, rotating polyhedron, with
    hidden lines removed, or a solid-fill polyhedron with hidden faces
    removed. There are a number of different polyhedra available; adding a new
    polyhedron to the program is quite simple.

